notes.p: The model reproduces the steady-state fluxes and metabolite concentrations of the branched model as given in Table 4 of the paper. For Vmax values, please note that there is a conversion factor of 270 to convert from U/mg-protein to mmol/min-Lcytosol as shown in Table 1 of the paper. For ADH the Keq given in the paper is for the reverse reaction and hence in the forward direction is 1/Keq. The model was successfully tested on MathSBML
